                "ULTIMATE SPACE SOLDIERS GEAR: Defenders of our solar system and unknown galaxies beyond, your little boys and girls are busy fighting evil galactic villains—after dinner and homework of course—and so, to ensure they’re prepared and to keep their imaginative storytelling pretend play running at top speed, they’ll need the latest KidFun Space Soldier Toy Gun Galaxy Blaster with colorful spinning lights and fast-paced super sonic sound effects to ensure victory and a safe journey home!",
                "SOUNDS & LIGHTS: Made from durable plastic construction to withstand hours of pretend play, the toy gun space soldier galaxy blaster is lightweight, featuring bright lights and cool blasting sound effects to add all the thrill to their latest mission; the toy gun also features a detachable magazine that rotates and flashes bright, multicolored LED lights, for even more intergalactic fighting fun",
                "FAST ACTION TOY BLASTER: This is where the fun begins! Upon release of the fast-acting trigger, the space soldier toy gun starts an awesome display of colorful, spinning bright lights, then followed by very cool sonic blasting firing sounds, that make saving the galaxy even more fun; the toy gun comes WITH batteries included, so the superhero action can start right out of the box!",
